          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "While 此模型 is leading a unit, ranged weapons equipped by 該單位中的模型 have the [ASSAULT] ability and melee weapons equipped by 該單位中的模型 have the [LANCE] ability.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "夫奧爾 斯艾 克阿恩!",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "143-1a21-8afb-16c4"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "每當 此模型 destroys an enemy 角色 model, you gain 1CP",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "特爾奧夫伊 特阿克爾",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "bbb5-617e-a254-8463"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "This model 可加入以下單位:\n\n■ 突擊 Intercessor Squad\n■ Bladeguard Veteran Squad\n■ Intercessor Squad\n■ Sternguard Veteran Squad\n■ Tactical Squad\n■ Company Heroes",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "領袖",
            "typeId": "9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64",
            "typeName": "Abilities",
            "hidden": false,
            "id": "90b4-a746-de9b-2df2"
          },
          {
            "characteristics": [
              {
                "$text": "If you include 此模型 in your army, until the end of the battle, non-角色 models in Outrider Squad units 你軍隊中的 have an 目標控制 characteristic of 3 while they are not 戰鬥震懾ed.",
                "name": "說明",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573"
              }
            ],
            "name": "伊恩斯普伊爾伊恩格 克奧姆姆阿恩德爾",
